  "notes": "HAR-697 records current Shopify Admin 2026-04 behavior. Contrary to the original ticket text, 2026-04 deletes product-owned metafield definitions without `deleteAllAssociatedMetafields` and with the flag explicitly false, returns empty userErrors, and leaves associated product metafields in place. With the flag true, Shopify removes the associated product metafield. `MetafieldDefinitionUpdateInput` has no `id` or `type` field in 2026-04; changing namespace, key, or ownerType through the identifier-shaped input returns NOT_FOUND."
